{
  "texts": [
    "We used OLS to train a model with the combined Cell Painting dataset using the leave-cells-out validation scheme (see Methods).",
    "The parameter α for the label update rule was set to 0.03.",
    "Additionally, the label smoothing 55 parameter was set to 0.1.",
    "Gradient reversal layer (GRL) 40 is an approach to domain adaptation for representation learning.",
    "It works by adding an adversarial classifier in a separate network branch that classifies the known domains of data points."
  ]
}